Review_title: Oddly unsatisfying and annoyingly boring as it goes on...
Review_Text: Oddly unsatisfying and annoyingly boring as it goes on...Great musician but this documentary seems hollow, skewed towards certain albums and songs and sadly doesn't feel like a full in depth articulation and analysis of Roberta.Maybe when she passes away that will come....but for now it feels like a short promo.----Oddly unsatisfying and annoyingly boring as it goes on...Great musician but this documentary seems hollow, skewed towards certain albums and songs and sadly doesn't feel like a full in depth articulation and analysis of Roberta.Maybe when she passes away that will come....
